            "highlights": [
                {
                    "text": "tertium comparationis",
                    "date": "2025-06-30T01:08:20.708"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Dream is defined as the mental activity of the sleeper in as much as he is asleep",
                    "date": "2025-06-30T11:18:25.530"
                },
                {
                    "text": "dreaming is an extension of waking life. Our dreams are always linked to the ideas8 that occupied consciousness shortly beforehand",
